page.title: 14CUBS
page.content: 1 A cub pack is a kind of club.We start at 6:30pm and stay until 8:00pm. At cubs we play all sorts of games like tig and some assault courses and go to camp at Aldridge.We do lots of things at camp.We do tracking in the nearby woods.At night in the bunk beds all the other cubs mess about and do not go to sleep.Soon there will be another camp.In the cub hut we do some knot tieing and sometimes we go over to the park.When we get back we salute the flag and then Akela dismisses the pack and we go home.
